data.description: BETTER THAN NEW IS AN UNDERSTATEMENT! Exceptional curb appeal welcomes you to this immaculately maintained two story home nestled on a corner lot  in one of Plant City’s hidden treasures found in the beautiful pool community of Whispering Woods.  A MUST SEE …the home has been impeccably upgraded with exquisite attention to detail boast 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath, with bonus room on 2nd floor. The well appointed kitchen features granite counter tops with complimenting subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, oversized breakfast bar with stone accent that is great for bar style eating and a center island. Generous owners suite with ensuite bathroom offers dual sinks, garden tub and separate shower with private water closet. Open concept design. Tile thru-out. Sizeable secondary bedrooms. Structured lanai fully fenced back yard.  No CDD/-Low HOA. Community pool, trail and tot play area. Minutes from historical downtown Plant City. Easy access to I-4. Centrally located between Tampa and Lakeland which makes for easy commutes.
